    dc:creator "Vreven, Emmanuel; Zamba, Armel Ibala; Mamonekene, Victor; Geerinckx, Tom" ;
    dc:title "Notoglanidium pembetadi Vreven, Zamba, Mamonekene & Geerinckx, 2013, new species" ;
